show.description: Paper puppets, haunted brides, and gods with grudges—this isn't your average republic. When ancient spirits collide with modern chaos, one clueless hero must navigate death, debt, and the divine. Secret Chronicles of the Republic is where horror meets hilarity. Watch Now!
